{"tid":983270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國度縮男】胖女拍拖食唔飽！ 寺外發爛渣爆喊點收科？","createTime":"2019-01-15T21:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T03:56:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5410a37eac3ea49804f64a8060948e61897d33cc","tid":983270,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T21:51:00.000Z","msg":"重慶華岩寺風景區寺廟大門前，近日有一對男女竟大打出手，其中，身穿粉紅外套的微胖女子突然嚎啕大哭起來，且一發不可收拾。警方接報到場了解情況，原來兩人是情侶關係，趁臘八節專程到寺廟吃齋菜，但女友吃不飽，男友又不准加餸，二人便爭吵了起來。<br />\n事發於13日近下午5時。從現場影片可見，女子在佛門清靜地大哭不止，遊人紛紛過來探看究竟。警方到場後安撫女子說：「你莫哭，有甚麼事跟我說，我給你作主。」女子聞言，更變本加厲，放聲哭個痛快。<br />\n身旁的劉姓男友無奈地交代事件：「我帶她吃飯，她沒吃飽，我就說了她幾句。」警方聽到後教訓這名沒心肝的男友：「你帶人家出來吃就吃好點嘛，哄她回家吧。」最終，在警方和遊人的勸說下，劉男牽着女友的手一起回家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547560630_91d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547560630_91d6.jpg&h=16b61d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59146172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59146172&d=yy9IwgYhyIKe5sLzLST0IQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2453e7c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59146172&h=86e0f32b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59146172</a>"},{"pid":"0a3a4aeddf6fe9151885c9e8e340db612aea7a91","tid":983270,"uid":135060,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T21:56:28.000Z","msg":"微胖女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779f053dfebf376665224c3f347c285524150a3f","tid":983270,"uid":124491,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTim